wfHrv_Updates_Recs.Comments:
Due to the major flood, BK Leach waterfowl hunting will be self-registration this year.
Hunters are required to fill out a Waterfowl Hunter Tag (Gray Card).
All hunting must stop at 1:00pm
Hunters may not enter the refuge or the levees surrounding the refuge
ADA Blind may only be used by registered ADA hunters
Please be respectful of other hunters.
